There are two family of containers:

- My_Container and its children classes which allows to print out and save its contents 
  to an HDF file. This type of containers can store
  <B>heterogeneous</B> collection of objects. They are used in
  stroring lists of saved attributes and Fields
  in My_Particles and My_Fields classes

- My_Map which simply allows to get a pointer to an arrays. This type of containers 
  stores <B> homogeneous </B> collections of objects. They are used in
  storing
  map of Attributes in  My_Particles classes for easy initialization of Attributes. 	
.
